Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were abandoned by your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You were thrown away like trash,\Njust like your alcoholic dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you're at the dump, don't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:02.93,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Town Massacre
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Could you please leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want a drink, you're going to have to pay your tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want money, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's at least enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any alcohol that you can buy with the money you got from making your kid work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what happened to Conrad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mrs. Hillman's dog is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have the guts to fire a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a cowardly drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to conduct a search in this rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Merckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just call this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Merckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Merckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mer-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Merckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Laufer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Someone answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take your gun as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have the guts to fire a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a cowardly drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are countless bodies scattered around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Wim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot them, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They were always picking on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Everything is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and gather your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you get this gun from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well to make it here with that leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Call the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The phones don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He took my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it someone who lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know him. It was an outsider\NI had never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,First things first, we have to get you treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he one of your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How many men do you have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that quite a few guns were\Ndistributed around town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They even gave a gun to this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A gun! You didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're not trash."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't pay any attention to those creeps."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"You were put on this Earth for a reason."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You empowered him with those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't shoot his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All the bullets are still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He held on to everything you taught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's all right, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, there are dead bodies all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How many did you hand out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How many guns did you give out in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people took your guns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not make me angrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad things happen when I get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like our grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just like our dead grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Our grandson knew us so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just like our real grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When you wrote a letter to your dead grandson,\Nyou were really sending {\i1}him{\i0} information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He is probably after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right Mr. Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should we say, Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The heavy rain in the middle of South Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,continues to cause damage to Bayern and other surrounding regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You smoke too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I need something now that I've stopped drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You should quit smoking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter, what have you been drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Do you see the resemblance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tenma! Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to the police the next time they question me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They never believe the important parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm going to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm telling you this is the man. This is the man who is going to kill a monster by himself."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's going to come back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a list of some of the damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elgar River has run over it's banks,\Nand is stopping traffic in a few areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The trains to and from those regions\Nhave also been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, the phone connections\Nare weak in all the regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this e-mail three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,After talking with Dr. Gillen, we've decided that you should see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for you in Ruhenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave a name to what Johan is trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"The perfect suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Many innocent people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruhenheim. There is a town in\NSouth Germany by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is probably headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an odd feeling, Mr. Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought you were just\Na part of a man's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like one of the characters in your picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've conducted investigations by gathering\Nobjective data for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, I ignored the facts and took a\Njourney through that man's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As I put all the clues together, half for fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I met a man in the Czech Republic who made\Nfrequent visits to the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hand drawn post card you sent him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,signed with your real name, Klaus Poppe, KP.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found this place and found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an odd feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,like one of the characters from your\Nbooks had escaped from the pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,During my research, on the list of people\Nwho assisted Czech Republic refugees,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there was the name, Klaus Poppe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You fled here just before the Berlin Wall came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you running from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In East Germany, at 511 Kinderheim\Na place based on your design...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That is where I was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you try to run away from people like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what Johan's trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it's actually happening in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Another gunshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of dead people when we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and take me away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible now. All the traffic's been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been doing? You leave and come back and then take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of blood and gunpowder in this town makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. I ordered us some hot tea at the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It will all disappear when the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What will disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some conditions to letting you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gillen is coming with you, and we're not letting you have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And please do as I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieter and Eva, and you, Dr. Reichwine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Schubert, Karl and Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hide all the people that Johan knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to erase all memories of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better go before Dieter notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories of Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories of you, Dr. Reichwein...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories of Lotte and Carl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories of the Fortners...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories of Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have memories that I don't want to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I want to forget about the memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan... What about your memories of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let them disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His gun has been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who shot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There was gun fire all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some men came to arm the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point, the people of the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,all got guns and started shooting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to... go... get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At least save the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Save...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Save...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I heard that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was in 1995 from that brain surgeon's statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:17:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So you acknowledge that your logic was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's still the prime suspect in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is still just an imaginary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,An imaginary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,During this vacation, the words that\Ncaught my attention are these,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"How does a real person become an imaginary one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate all those who know the person and\Nall those who know of that person's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he will become like the end\Nof your books, Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"He finally had a name, but all the people who could call him by that name disappeared."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"And Johan was such a wonderful name, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What if that's what's happening in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'd do if I was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also an imaginary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the man called Mr. Neumeyer,\Nwho signed the hotel registry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,nor am I the man known as Wolfgang Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll disappear, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with all the others whom had their\Nmemories and names taken from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting here for my judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I don't know how to pay for what I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to just accept everything that happens here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You were waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you scared of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand how serious your crime is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what it means to destroy\Na person's sense of good and evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happens when you\Nawaken the monster inside of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,People need to think that food is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,People need to enjoy a picnic on their day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People need to cherish the beer they have after work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,People... People are supposed to feel sorrow from\Nthe bottom of their heart when a child dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get you out of this town and make\Nyou tell everyone all that you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show the world the true nature\Nof the monster you have awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be someone orchestrating this carnage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Another gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See. I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry. I'll take you to the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The man giving the orders is at the Bergbach Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only have one gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These two were outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All I did was win the lotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we had told people earlier that we found Conrad's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Before this town went mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't shot any of them even once. I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow these.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You protect this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The residents have guns, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective. I can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When this job is over, buy me a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.72,0:22:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Live!
